INSERT INTO `info_mix` (`id`, `img`, `name`, `content`, `title`, `keyword`, `description`) VALUES
(1, '/mix/view/admin/Themes/kcfinder/upload/images/danhmuctour/grand-canyon-national-park-362695.jpg', 'About us', '<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(60, 59, 59); font-family: Arial;">\r\n	<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">1. Who we are?</strong></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(60, 59, 59); font-family: Arial;">\r\n	Located in Hanoi, the capital city of Vietnam, Mix Tourist is a local tour operator based in Vietnam, specialized in tailor made inbound package tours for individuals, small groups and large ones to Vietnam. With many years of experience in tourism along with constant efforts of officers and staff to make excellent services with the most preferential price, we&rsquo;re the reliable for partners and customers.</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(60, 59, 59); font-family: Arial;">\r\n	<img alt="" height="351" src="http://mixtourist.com/uploads/images/August/logomixtourist.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: none; display: block;" width="600" /></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(60, 59, 59); font-family: Arial;">\r\n	The Mix Tourist team provides professional and attentive service for holiday, corporate, special interest and cruise travel. Members of the team have lived and travelled intensively throughout Vietnam and it would be hard to find a region that at least one of the team hasn&rsquo;t travelled to! We recognize the importance of careful planning and we have the skills and knowledge to help you get the best out of your travel experience. Our genuine love of all things travel means that whether it be travel by plane, cruise ship, self-drive, we can ensure your plans run smoothly and you have the most amazing journey &ndash; and we love when you come back and share your precious memories with us. As a result, we have a lot of repeat visitors and they are willing to recommend us. That&rsquo;s the way we have been developing company so far.</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(60, 59, 59); font-family: Arial;">\r\n	Come along and explore one of the most beautiful magnificient sights in the world!</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(60, 59, 59); font-family: Arial;">\r\n	We are very happy to welcome you to our beautiful country!</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(60, 59, 59); font-family: Arial;">\r\n	<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">2. What we do?</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />\r\n	<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />\r\n	- Provide full useful travel information &amp; high quality travel services&nbsp; in Vietnam, Laos and Cambodia<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />\r\n	<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />\r\n	- Provide the tailor-made holidays and private tours with different styles<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />\r\n	<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />\r\n	- Make the hotel bookings throughout Indochina at affordable price<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />\r\n	<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />\r\n	- Offer quality private transportation throughout Indochina<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />\r\n	<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />\r\n	- Arrange Visa services<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />\r\n	<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />\r\n	- Provide MICE services<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />\r\n	<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />\r\n	- Make the air ticket &amp; train ticket booking<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />\r\n	<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />\r\n	-&nbsp; Provide professional Interpreter, Translator and Tour guide<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />\r\n	<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />\r\n	<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">3. Why travel with us?</strong></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(60, 59, 59); font-family: Arial;">\r\n	From the beginning, we have maintained the strong values which have brought our company from strength to strength. Not losing sights of our commitment to service and customer satisfaction, we have cultivated a brand name with excellence, quality and value. Our tour offers you the very best that the region has to offer in term of accommodation, transportation, food, tour guide, sightseeing and enriched cultural experiences.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color: rgb(60, 59, 59); font-family: Arial;">- Interesting Tailor- made Trip for all budgets</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(60, 59, 59); font-family: Arial;">\r\n	The well customized and interesting itinerary is our key point. As we live in Indochina, we know our place deeply. We believe that your tour should be full of cherished memories to take home. Embark on your dream holiday with the peace of mind that you are traveling with the experts who have knowledge and expertise to design and provide holidays to suit your interest</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(60, 59, 59); font-family: Arial;">\r\n	- Reasonable price</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(60, 59, 59); font-family: Arial;">\r\n	Our tours offer great value for money.We set up and maintain the solid relationships with major airlines, hotels and local service suppliers throughout Vietnam, Cambodia &amp; Laos. This enables us to offer a great variety of well designed and personalized tours at competitive&nbsp; price while keeping the high-quality services. We have no extra hidden costs.&nbsp; All inclusions and exclusions are mentioned at our final confirmation for your trip.<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />\r\n	<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />\r\n	- Our promise of SAFTY</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(60, 59, 59); font-family: Arial;">\r\n	We constantly monitor the region in case any problems should arise and all our guides have first aid training. We also require that all Asia View Travel&rsquo;s clients have adequate medical and travel insurance before participating in our tour programs. We take care and assist our customers before, during and after their holidays.</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(60, 59, 59); font-family: Arial;">\r\n	- Professional, knowledgable and friendly&nbsp; Team and Tour guides</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(60, 59, 59); font-family: Arial;">\r\n	With Mix Tourist you are always able to speak to a sales representative day or night. Drop us an email or call us 24 hours a day to speak to our dedicated team working to help you around the clock . Our team are happy to listen to your requirement and give you personal, friendly and expert suggestion based on your interest, schedule, budget, level of energy and travel preferences. Our staff are the local people who have deep knowledge about the region and willing to introduce it&rsquo;s beauty to you. Their expertise and years of travel experience makes them the reliable travel consultants and best tour operators.</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(60, 59, 59); font-family: Arial;">\r\n	- Reliable and authorized Tour Operator in Vietnam</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(60, 59, 59); font-family: Arial;">\r\n	We have been operating under the control of Vietnam National Administration of Tourism and have International Tour Operator Licence issued by Vietnam National Administration of Tourism. We are proud to say that we are the reliable and authorized Tour Operator in Vietnam.</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(60, 59, 59); font-family: Arial;">\r\n	<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">4. Our tour Categories</strong></p>\r\n<ul style="margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(60, 59, 59); font-family: Arial;">\r\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">\r\n		From Luxury to Standard&nbsp; Classic Tours &amp; Family holiday: Cultural, Historical, Natural discovery</li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">\r\n		Special interest tours: Honeymoon, Culinary Tour, Beach holiday, Golf Tour, Educational Tour</li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">\r\n		Halong bay cruises &amp; Mekong river cruises</li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">\r\n		Adventure&nbsp; Tours: Trekking, cycling, diving , Kayaking &amp; exploration more</li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">\r\n		Multi-Country Tours: Vietnam , Laos &amp; Cambodia</li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">\r\n		Free &amp; Easy packages</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'About us', 'About us', 'About us'),
